com.excite.atm.impl

Class Constants

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.excite.atm.impl.Constants

  • public class Constants
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains certain constant values used by the application. Naming convention followed : FN_ File name. _APP_PROP_KEY A key to the data available in properties file. ERR_ Error code prefix.
    Author:
    James David
